{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2914827466","title":"浙江省黄岩县路桥镇利丰大队生活状况调查资料（草稿）","origin":"浙江省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c7b57c739f","index":0,"year":1961,"month":4,"day":23,"articleId":"2914827466"}],"tags":[{"id":"36a2aad2bd","name":"黄岩","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2300058d24","type":"title","text":"浙江省黄岩县路桥镇利丰大队生活状况调查资料（草稿）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"0648c081d9","type":"paragraph","text":"解放以后到一九五八年，群众的物质文化水平是逐年提高的，大家是满意的。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"c26d9da4c4","type":"paragraph","text":"公社化后，特别是一九五九至一九六○两年，由于生产减产，收入减少，征购任务增加，社员生活发生严重困难，普遍出现吃草、吃糠，饿、病、逃、荒，妻离子散，家破人亡。社员说这二年有十个多：“吃草、吃粮多；生病多；死人多；出卖东西多；送儿送女多；妇女改嫁多；全家破亡多；人口外流多；讨饭多；偷窃多”。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"f360af8228","type":"subtitle","text":"（一）大量出卖农具家具：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"a9d2ac2156","type":"paragraph","text":"据二、五两个小队17户初步调查，社员为了买私粮吃，每户都有出卖。一九五九年共出卖各种家具农具34件，计176．4元；一九六○年共出卖各种农具家具135件，计445．6元。这些家具中有较大的床、橱、箱、帐、被、席床、蓑衣到球鞋、镜子、帽子、锅等小东西，甚至拆房屋、卖口粮，样样都有。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"66faf32621","type":"paragraph","text":"据一户典型户的破产状况调查来看，破产的程度是严重的。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"f4d29f6993","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡胜寿（老中农），公社化前，全家十二人，三个男正劳动力，吃饭分三家，家里大小家具齐全。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"a53d88e24c","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年春，口粮不足，社里又没有钱，为了买蕃薯丝吃，逐渐开始出卖家具。在当时家里还有一些积蓄，所以出卖东西不多。五九（主要是三至五月）一年中，出卖家具五件，计13元。其中：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"7e64946a1b","type":"paragraph","text":"席床二件4元，织布机一部4元，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"5f47bee00c","type":"paragraph","text":"铜火炉一个3元，铜盆一个2元，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"6ca64582ed","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年九月十一日，大儿子蔡小玉，因患浮肿病死去，当时剩下老婆和一个八岁的女儿、四岁的小儿。二儿子蔡小头生了严重的浮肿病。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"16981eb251","type":"paragraph","text":"到一九六○年春，全家十一个人，每人每天用粮只有五两大米，吃不饱，到路桥买一角二分一斤的菜叶、一角到一角五分一斤的蕃莳藤，补充口粮。价格昂贵，家里又没有了钱，因此，只得廉价大量变卖家具。六○年（主要是上半年）一年中，共出卖26件，计117．6元。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"8ad1d1c410","type":"paragraph","text":"其中：床一张    22元  桌一张   66元     箱橱一只      4元","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"258a0c6021","type":"paragraph","text":"箱二只    4元   棉被二条 12元     布帐二顶      24元","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"6a6bfba75c","type":"paragraph","text":"衣二件    13元  月桶二只  6．8元  脚桶一只      2元","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"0389a12174","type":"paragraph","text":"汤桶一只  3元， 便桶一只  2元     摇篮摇车四件  5．5元","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"1d38d040df","type":"paragraph","text":"黄铜三斤  3元   锅一只    1．8元  镜子一面      1．5元","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"f0bd75249d","type":"paragraph","text":"球鞋一双  3元   帽一顶    1元     布一丈        3元。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"098fe98393","type":"paragraph","text":"集体食堂烧饭，每斤米要一角六分（包括柴费），又拆去谷仓门二个和部分楼板当柴烧。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"e1bd556823","type":"paragraph","text":"在六○年三月，大媳妇改嫁外乡；到六月分，又带走二个小孩。这样，全家由十二人，剩下八个人，弄得家破人亡，东西卖掉。目前，家里为了买米买柴，还在陆续出卖东西。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"e2b14ccd78","type":"paragraph","text":"其次，家庭副业大大减少。公社化前，全家有席床三具，一年可打席1080张，约计可收432元，养肉猪二只，可收123元，自留地种菜可收36元，仅三项合计可收入591元，每人平均有49．25元。公社化后，二只猪给生产队捉去归蓄牧场，自己不养了，打席无席草，织帽不会织，都没有收入。唯一的是在上半年三、四月，挖田荠出卖收入12元。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"6e64a0fd0a","type":"subtitle","text":"（二）疾病严重：","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"d58b7fccee","type":"paragraph","text":"据省医疗队普查：全大队二百二十三户732人中，患有各种疾病的有189人，占总人口的26％，其中贫农124人，中农63人，富农1人，地主1人。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"bebaa6c819","type":"paragraph","text":"主要疾病有：","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"870384c5a1","type":"paragraph","text":"浮肿病：78人（其中干瘦的28人）","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"5789596c89","type":"paragraph","text":"其中：25岁以下     6人","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"3d623ec3af","type":"paragraph","text":"25—30岁     6人","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"e2d2b45738","type":"paragraph","text":"30—35岁    10人","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"39c5e46565","type":"paragraph","text":"35—40岁    13人","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"16287472d7","type":"paragraph","text":"40岁以上    54人","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"a59c288ab7","type":"paragraph","text":"妇女病（闭经）62人（其中已治疗来潮11人）","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"21f2b536a0","type":"paragraph","text":"其中：25岁以下    10人","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"f3f3c2970e","type":"paragraph","text":"25—30岁    22人","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"ca401f6f6d","type":"paragraph","text":"30—35岁    20人","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"b1330bee3f","type":"paragraph","text":"30—40岁左右 10人","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"58b597065d","type":"paragraph","text":"子宫下垂：36人","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"e6f512ad64","type":"paragraph","text":"其中：30岁以下   9人","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"ef53514c98","type":"paragraph","text":"30—40岁  11人","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"6425c0deb0","type":"paragraph","text":"40岁以上  16人","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"660d5afe07","type":"paragraph","text":"小儿营养不良：13人","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"0fe8d1f6de","type":"paragraph","text":"2—4岁    7人","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"f2189643cc","type":"paragraph","text":"5—6岁    6人","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"3a344184ba","type":"subtitle","text":"（三）死亡多、生育少：","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"b9e5e38576","type":"paragraph","text":"据六个小队83户调查：","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"7ccd190ce7","type":"paragraph","text":"非正常死亡：59年  4人","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"d82f5533d7","type":"paragraph","text":"60年  23人。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"678d6e5b3b","type":"paragraph","text":"合计27人，其中5个中年人主要是生浮肿病致死，9个小孩是因母亲吃粮少断奶致死，9个较年老的因吃草加底子差而致死。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"7dca40dc51","type":"paragraph","text":"生育显著减少：","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"2d2e2e8aa3","type":"paragraph","text":"互助组一年，生小孩  18个","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"af03be385f","type":"paragraph","text":"初级社一年   ”     8个","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"517bf38182","type":"paragraph","text":"高级社一年   ”     31个","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"96701b0faa","type":"paragraph","text":"58  年       ”     8个","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"87ce491386","type":"paragraph","text":"59  年       ”     4个","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"48f8587327","type":"paragraph","text":"60   年      ”     5个。（都是干部家属）","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"091bf81177","type":"subtitle","text":"（四）体质下降：","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"bc55f45a6f","type":"paragraph","text":"据第二小队调查，公社化前有十个男正劳动力，五九年生浮肿病死一个。现有九个劳力中：公社化前，个个身体健康，普遍能挑重担。从生产队到路桥，最少的可以挑120斤，最多的能挑200斤，三里路中途不要休息。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"0a084bcaa7","type":"paragraph","text":"现在，有四个患病，大家体力普遍下降一半左右，同样的路程，能挑100斤的只有4个，挑50—90斤的5个。而且中途要休息二、三次。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"},{"id":"e848ef99e1","type":"paragraph","text":" 黄岩县路桥镇利丰大队一九六一年四月廿三日","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466"}],"page":{"id":"dce8199c22","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"2914827466","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}